text: Parahyponomeuta egregiella is a moth of the family Yponomeutidae. It is known from the Iberian Peninsula, Italy, Sardinia, Corsica, France, Switzerland and Luxembourg. ==References== ==External links== *lepiforum.de Category:Moths described in 1838 Category:Yponomeutidae Category:Moths of Europe pt:Parahyponomeuta vi:Parahyponomeuta
